works.description: With the escalating price of fuel, people are choosing bicycles over motor vehicles for short distances. But, if uber rich people think these bikes are not meant for the elite class, then they must have a look at some expensive bikes, like the Renovo r4 pursuit, Art-Veil bike or the beautiful Mahogany Bikes from Sanomagic. All these bikes are made of elegant wood and are perfect for an eco-friendly ride. The latest addition in the beautiful yet functional wooden bikes has come from Lagomorph design. The fully functional single-speed wooden bike boasts a frame made of special American Black Walnut.
